{"tid":267781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想買日本電器..想知我用唔用得呢個變壓器？","createTime":"2017-06-02T13:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T14:16:47.000Z","uid":65236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76da452e709b7892aedc9edc0fc34642ef82b6cf","tid":267781,"uid":65236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:58:26.000Z","msg":"我本身有個成個鞋盒咁大既變壓器<br />\n一直都係for日本電器用緊既: 100v轉220v(50/60Hz) 1500w<br />\n<br />\n而家想買個電器都係100v轉220v(50/60Hz)<br />\n但就只係400w<br />\n<br />\n其實我個變壓器大咁多怕唔怕架??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我google過架但呢個情況搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba52d7abcc73383947e460829dbded0e2ea9062d","tid":267781,"uid":3232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e5ebcc564b1705a6086c4b78dc490340c507ee","tid":267781,"uid":57117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:11:17.000Z","msg":"只可以少過1500W"},{"pid":"4e1b42220094633260f331101ea8806a3ef133b0","tid":267781,"uid":2053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"你手上有1500，<br />\n而你想又用左用400買嘢，<br />\n咁你認為你買唔買到？"},{"pid":"e5257ee51033138c886a00fc6f27754f6c4099af","tid":267781,"uid":65236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只可以少過1500W</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我搵到人話 電器1000<br />\n變壓器1500比較好 2000最好<br />\n<br />\n姐係變壓器大過電器w數就無死?姐係小過幾多都無問題？<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"f3eff4296e0f6fb450fd5ea6b7ab5b200812e0c8","tid":267781,"uid":65236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T14:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你手上有1500，<br />\n而你想又用左用400買嘢，<br />\n咁你